  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634090/extras/33e9e587adb2cf6b1b7b468db4ba0ecd.poster.avif?t=1627314899\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634090/extras/33e9e587adb2cf6b1b7b468db4ba0ecd.webm?t=1627314899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634090/extras/33e9e587adb2cf6b1b7b468db4ba0ecd.mp4?t=1627314899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Arcade racing game</h2><strong>Mini Racing World</strong> is a low poly arcade racing game with a career, car tuning and a open world map to explore!<br>It has a <strong>simple and immediate</strong> driving model, but difficult to master.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634090/extras/ac66ddd7473adb0756fe1db80b87029b.poster.avif?t=1627314899\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634090/extras/ac66ddd7473adb0756fe1db80b87029b.webm?t=1627314899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >18 different vehicles</h2>You can buy new cars with the <strong>credits</strong> you gain by playing the events. Every car has a <strong>different driving style</strong> and different components to customize it. You can also unlock some components by completing certain events.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634090/extras/1713a477085244e3488dfee3df0c2549.poster.avif?t=1627314899\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634090/extras/1713a477085244e3488dfee3df0c2549.webm?t=1627314899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634090/extras/1713a477085244e3488dfee3df0c2549.mp4?t=1627314899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Car customization</h2>Modify your cars by changing color, exhaust, spoilers and other aesthetic components. <br>Improve the perfomance of your vehicle to be able to proceed during the career.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634090/extras/c10055b881369fd8a03fd069e2dd1029.poster.avif?t=1627314899\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634090/extras/c10055b881369fd8a03fd069e2dd1029.webm?t=1627314899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634090/extras/c10055b881369fd8a03fd069e2dd1029.mp4?t=1627314899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Career subdivided in seasons and a mini open world to explore</h2>Become the Mini Racing World champion by winning <strong>seasons</strong> and special races.<br>Explore a diverse mini <strong>open world</strong> to access the events and the garage.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634090/extras/805b297804ea70c89568da9856dd19ab.poster.avif?t=1627314899\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634090/extras/805b297804ea70c89568da9856dd19ab.webm?t=1627314899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634090/extras/805b297804ea70c89568da9856dd19ab.mp4?t=1627314899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Low poly colorful graphics</h2>3D <strong>low poly graphics</strong> with colorful and stylized environment and cars.<br>Vehicles out of proportion for maximum cuteness.",
